description:
Do we ever stop moving?! Neil deGrasse Tyson breaks down all the ways we are moving throughout the universe, from Earth's rotation, precession, to the Milky Way galaxy’s movement toward the Great Attractor.

08:26 - Can You Feel It? 
09:00 - Earth & the Moon
10:17 - Closing
